AP209 Viewer

  • This is an example of visualizing a STEP AP209 finite element model. The visualization was generated by the NIST STEP File Analyzer and rendered with X3DOM.
  • Use the mouse to rotate, pan, and zoom. Use Page Down to switch between perspective and orthographic views.
  • An example of an AP209 model generated from a NIST CAD model
